      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/jane-street-scores-10-6-billion-trading-haul-amid-growth-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Jane Street Group LLC 去年的净交易收入为 106 亿美元——这是证明其作为主要做市商的存在并着眼于进一步增长的众多数字之一。]]></description>
